<https://example.org/genericontology> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Thing> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Thing> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Top-level root class for all entities."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Entity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Entity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Thing> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Entity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Any identifiable entity in the ontology."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Agent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Agent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Entity> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Agent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An entity capable of acting or participating in activities."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Person> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Agent> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Person> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#disjointWith> <https://example.org/genericontology/Organization> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A human individual."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/ProfessionalPerson> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/ProfessionalPerson> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Person> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/ProfessionalPerson> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A person who performs a professional role."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/SpecialistPerson> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/SpecialistPerson> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/ProfessionalPerson> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/SpecialistPerson> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A professional person with a specialized role."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Operator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Operator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/SpecialistPerson> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Operator> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#disjointWith> <https://example.org/genericontology/Technician> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Operator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A specialist person who operates systems or equipment."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Technician> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Technician> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/SpecialistPerson> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Technician> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#disjointWith> <https://example.org/genericontology/Operator> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Technician> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A specialist person who maintains or repairs systems or equipment."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Manager> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Manager> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/ProfessionalPerson> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Manager> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A professional person who manages people or resources."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Organization> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Organization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Agent> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Organization> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#disjointWith> <https://example.org/genericontology/Person> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Organization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A structured collective agent such as a company or institution."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Department> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Department> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Organization> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Department> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A subdivision of an organization."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Facility> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Facility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Entity> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Facility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A physical place or site used for operations."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Site> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Facility> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A specific physical site or location."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Building> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Building> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Site> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Building> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A constructed building at a site."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Room> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Room> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Building> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Room> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A room within a building."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Asset> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Asset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Entity> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Asset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A valuable resource owned or used by an organization."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Equipment> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Equipment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://example.org/genericontology/Asset> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Equipment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A physical piece of equipment."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/genericontology/Machine> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
